      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is not crazy to feel that letting go would give them freedom, but the idea that your life is a burden to them is a story they have never heard from you. Please consider that your presence, even with its struggles, is the only thing keeping them grounded in the reality they were raised in. You cannot choose to leave them behind, and the guilt of doing so would be far heavier than the pain of staying.",
